CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 25, 1961, pg. B5 reads: "Enjoying Chi Affair - More Chi's and their guests, who enjoyed the swank affair at the Pittsburgh Hilton are shown in these three photographs...Some of the guests at the table of Dr. and Mrs. Charles Bookert, are, left to right: Mrs. Charles Witten, Dr. Charles Witten of Detroit, Mich.; Mrs. Charles Bookert, Mrs. Jack Moore, Jack Moore, Dr. Bookert, Dr. William Hunt, Mrs. Albert Rosenberg, Mrs. William Hunt and Dr. Rosenberg..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Mrs. and Dr. Charles Witten, Mrs. Charles Bookert, Mrs. and Mr. Jack Moore, Dr. Bookert, Dr. William Hunt, Mrs. Albert Rosenberg, Mrs. William Hunt, and Dr. Rosenberg, seated at banquet table in Hilton Hotel for Chi Delta Mu supper dance
